                <span class="text-gray-600">Type B Unit (796 sqft):</span>
                <span class="font-semibold">RM5,400-6,600/month income</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-gray-600">iHousing Management:</span>
                <span class="font-semibold">RM250/month (flat fee)</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-gray-600">Annual Net Income:</span>
