              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-gray-600">vs Traditional (20%):</span>
                <span class="font-bold text-red-600">Save RM9,600/year!</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a href="/parkland/roi-calculator/" class="inline-block bg-white text-green-700 font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg mt-4 hover:bg-gray-100">
              Calculate Your Exact ROI â†’
            </a>
